description:
420 Presents:

Album: Farm
Artist: Dinosaur Jr.

Dinosaur Jr. has re-staked their place in indie, pop and rock music with Farm 
and done so in the best possible fashion: they've pushed their established sound harder than they 
ever have previously and just powered through without looking back. In the simplest of terms, 
Dinosaur Jr. proved that they could return on Beyond and that they could still be vital but, on Farm, 
they actually are back, do sound vital and clearly have captivating muses worth chasing. 
The proof of all of those things lies in all twelve of Farm's tracks; fans can only hope they do it 
more than just this once.
